OL,3,CGosport parents given 48 hours notice
OL,4,Cof their children's preschool closing
OL,6,FParents say they're frustrated and
OL,7,Fupset after the sudden closure of
OL,8,Ftheir children's pre-school.
OL,10,FLittle Explorers Nursery in Gosport
OL,11,Fhas terminated all pre-school places -
OL,12,Ffollowing an Ofsted inspection that
OL,13,Fhighlighted safeguarding and health
OL,14,Fand safety concerns.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, Little Explorers nursery
OL,17,Ftold parents that while the nursery
OL,18,Fwould remain open, after today, its
OL,19,Fpreschool would no longer exist.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
