PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775934664
OL,3,CGosport parents given 48 hours notice
OL,4,Cof their children's preschool closing
OL,6,FThe nursery say it's due to staffing
OL,7,Fshortfalls and is working with
OL,8,Ffamilies and the local council to help
OL,9,Fthem find alternative provisions.
OL,11,FJodie Edwards is one of 42 parents
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,FHer 4-year-old twins and one-year-old
OL,15,Fbaby had loved going to the pre-
OL,16,Fschool, but now Jodie has had to move
OL,17,Fthem to another site in the town.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775934664
OL,3,CGosport parents given 48 hours notice
OL,4,Cof their children's preschool closing
OL,6,FShe said: "It's been horrible not only
OL,7,Ffinding a replacement, but actually
OL,8,Fgoing and seeing the staff there.
OL,9,FThey've all just been just as upset as
OL,10,Fus. It's been horrific all around."
OL,12,F" I've made the personal choice to
OL,13,Ftell the kids as little as possible.
OL,15,F"I know some parents have told their
OL,16,Fkids as close to the truth as they
OL,17,Fcan, and the children have just been
OL,18,Fasking, what did I do wrong? Like, is
OL,19,Fit my fault? Which is obviously awful,
OL,20,Fbecause it's not their fault and it's
OL,21,Fhorrible."
OL,26,@rD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
