PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775934664
OL,3,CGosport parents given 48 hours notice
OL,4,Cof their children's preschool closing
OL,6,FA welfare notice was issued to Little
OL,7,FExplorers Nursery following an Ofsted
OL,8,Finspection of the pre-school in March.
OL,10,FIn their report, inspectors found
OL,11,Fsafeguarding issues, health and safety
OL,12,Fconcerns, and instances of special
OL,13,Feducational needs not being met.
OL,15,FLocal MP Dame Caroline Dinenage says
OL,16,Fthe system needs to change.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
