FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775934664
OL,3,CGosport parents given 48 hours notice
OL,4,Cof their children's preschool closing
OL,6,F"With 48 hours notice, this has been a
OL,7,Fdisaster...So I'm meeting with
OL,8,FHampshire County Council to see what
OL,9,Fcan be done to, find alternative
OL,10,Fplaces for these youngsters in an
OL,11,Femergency.
OL,13,F"Second thing is to speak with Ofsted.
OL,14,FI can't understand how we got to a
OL,15,Fposition where with just 48 hours
OL,16,Fnotice, parents were given this
OL,17,Finformation. "
OL,26,@yD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
