PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775934664
OL,3,CGosport parents given 48 hours notice
OL,4,Cof their children's preschool closing
OL,6,FLittle Explorers Nursery have said:
OL,7,F"This decision has not been taken
OL,8,Flightly; however, due to current
OL,9,Fstaffing constraints, we are unable to
OL,10,Fsafely accommodate all children while
OL,11,Fadhering to required ratios.
OL,13,F"We understand that this news may be
OL,14,Fupsetting and inconvenient, and we
OL,15,Fsincerely apologise for the impact
OL,16,Fthis may have on families."
OL,18,FJodie says the community has rallied
OL,19,Fround with parents offering each other
OL,20,Fchildcare support.
OL,26,@xD@[O]
